<plot>Dan has returned from the university weak and lazy. His father wants to toughen him up so he hires a tramp to pick a fight. This doesn't work, but when the tramp starts paying attention to a young heiress, Dan resolves to toughen up and win the heiress for himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?125315</url></doc>
